org.testng

Interface ITestNGMethod

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseTestMethod, ClonedMethod, ConfigurationMethod, FactoryMethod, JUnit3TestMethod, JUnit4TestMethod, JUnitTestMethod, TestNGMethod

    public interface ITestNGMethod
extends java.lang.Comparable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Describes a TestNG annotated method and the instance on which it will be invoked. This interface is not meant to be implemented by users.
